Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.38,0:00:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A magazine page I can't finish reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to read it, but somehow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.23,0:00:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Game software is stacked in the corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.01,0:00:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't play them, will they become meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm just beyond the table, and I'm trying to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A never changing facial expression is on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.14,0:00:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though I'm right here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.94,0:00:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They can't reach, they can't reach, these feelings of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.13,0:01:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what's really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Final Duel!\N Yugi VS Pegasus!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.54,0:01:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.83,0:01:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'm counting on you, my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.96,0:01:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Grandpa, at last, the fight\N against Pegasus will begin...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.31,0:01:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll win for sure and get your soul back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.05,0:01:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen. In important, stressful situations,\N a Duelist's heart will begin to lose grip.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.74,0:01:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You begin to lose sight of yourself,\N and before you know it, you begin\N walking down the path of failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}Yugi, if you are able to face your\N﻿heart in these times of pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}You'll be able to win for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.20,0:02:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}I understand, Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.42,0:02:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yugi, it's finally about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.09,0:02:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You made it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.88,0:02:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You have to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.80,0:02:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For your grandfather and Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿And for Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.43,0:02:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It is time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.10,0:02:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Challenger Yugi Mutou,\N please enter the Duel Ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.12,0:02:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}Here I come, Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.76,0:03:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yugi! We're counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Show him your power, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.74,0:03:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}At long last,\N the final showdown has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}My cards, we're about to face the master\N﻿of the kingdom, the strongest Duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}Let's fight as one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yugi boy, you are indeed \Na splendid Duelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.61,0:03:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I commend you on surviving\N the fights in this kingdom ﻿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.21,0:04:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿and earning the right\N to challenge me to this fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before we Duel, you will \Nswear to me right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That if I win, you'll return\N my grandpa's soul to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yes, it's a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The souls of the Kaiba brothers\N sealed in the cards as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.88,0:04:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Well, isn't this odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Is Kaiba boy not your enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Right now, {\i1}you're{\i0} my only enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But then, what can {\b0}I{\b1} do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You don't have to steal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will defeat Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I swore to Mokuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}That I would allow him to\N see his brother once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I see. An oath, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}The Mind Scan...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Okay, I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:04:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿If you should win this match...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I will set them free from\N the prison of lost souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's finally starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I can almost see their fighting spirits clashing from all the way up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.01,0:05:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yeah! We finally made it this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Will Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0} be alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The odds of winning against an opponent\N who can use the ﻿power of the\N Millennium Eye to read his mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You dumbass! Yugi won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿He'll be the {\i1}real{\i0} king of this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.16,0:05:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿He'll kick that Pegasus bastard's ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That's right! That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.03,0:05:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Honda?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just brightened the mood!\N What's with the depressing attitude, Honda?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.67,0:05:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿But just think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.71,0:05:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿This battle can't be called fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.09,0:05:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿He's taken those three hostage\N﻿to lure Yugi this far, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿But didn't Pegasus capture his grandfather's\N﻿soul just for this Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Pegasus is a Duelist himself.\N Even {\i1}he{\i0} wouldn't do anything that low.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:05:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.31,0:06:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Besides, {\i1}you're{\i0}\N the one most worried here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Their Duel is about to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Hey, let's go to the upper balcony\N so we can see it better!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.78,0:06:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yeah, good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} and Anzu-{\i1}chan{\i0}\N aren't worried at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.79,0:06:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you may be right, Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Pegasus isn't to be underestimated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿If the Duel gets dangerous for him, there's\N﻿no telling what measures he'll take.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0}, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything\N about his grandfather's soul,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if I can at least save Mokuba and\N﻿Kaiba, Yugi may stand a better chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}Mokuba, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi Mutou, you have come to Duelist Kingdom\N﻿in order to challenge the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Please show me the Honor of the\N﻿King's Left card as your entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yeah. This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.32,0:06:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Honor of the Kings Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿If you hold that card...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿..and you are able to\N defeat the king of Duelist Kingdom,﻿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:07:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus J. Crawford,\N in a game of Duel Monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Pegasus will hand you 60%\N of Industrial Illusion's stocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿In other words, if you wish it,\N you will become the ﻿new president\N of Industrial Illusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Are you {\i1}serious{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(319,447)}﻿Huh? Where's Honda?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.94,0:07:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Dunno... He wandered off on his\N﻿own somewhere and took off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿He probably had to use the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.07,0:07:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Anyway, the Duel's about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That is a truly amazing present!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿For the one able to defeat me, of course\N﻿there should be a reward of such mass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Or you're just confident there's no one\N alive that {\i1}can{\i0} defeat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿However, it takes\N great risk to gain such honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That card, Honor of the King's Left...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿There is no image on the card.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:08:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿And do you know {\i1}why{\i0}, Yugi boy...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿An image will appear on the card\N once you are defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿In other words,\N my soul will be sealed in the card?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Just like Kaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'm prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That courage is magnificent!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.04,0:08:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿If Yugi loses, \Nhe'll end up just like Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿He...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Even though he knew what would happen, he\N﻿still went ahead and challenged Pegasus?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿He's betting his own soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.47,0:08:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Can he really do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno... But he definitely did something\N ﻿to Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} and Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}Yugi... don't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.32,0:08:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}If you lose, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}You {\b0}have{\b1} to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It's too bad, Pegasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:09:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I have no intention of becoming\N﻿a part of your card collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}I am not going to defeat you\N merely for the sake ﻿of adding\N another card to my collection...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}My most {\b0}important{\b1} goal lies in getting\N﻿control of Kaiba Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿This fight will decide\N the future of Kaiba Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.56,0:09:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like it if\N Mr. Pegasus could dispose of Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we need now\N to complete the contract is to\N find the key Mokuba hid away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Kaiba Corporation, Mr. Pegasus,\N will then become yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}All the pieces are in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}All that remains is to win this Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Now then, the Duelist Kingdom \NChampionship Match will now begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Cut and shuffle each other's cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.65,0:10:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.21,0:10:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}Yugi boy... with the power of\N the Millennium Eye at my disposal\N you have no chance of defeating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}I {\b0}can't{\b1} lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Bakura may just be right\N about all the stuff he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿If I find them, it will be a big help,\N﻿but this castle's so huge...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.52,0:11:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It's time to change shifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿How's the kid doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The same as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.69,0:11:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿We shouldn't have to worry about him escaping, but don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.11,0:11:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Of course. He's the only one who knows the location of our precious key, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.25,0:11:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}Mokuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Huh? It's a dead end?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.48,0:12:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Here I go! My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.46,0:12:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I set a card face-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Then I play this Monster Card\N in Defense Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.31,0:12:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}Does his Millennium Eye really allow him\N﻿to see my entire hand and set card?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:12:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It is my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I set a card face-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Furthermore...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.37,0:13:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿A Monster Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'll lay Archery Mermaid in Defense Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Turn over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Archery Mermaid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.01,0:13:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just a Normal Water-Attribute\N Monster Card?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}And he didn't even\N play her in Attack Mode...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.23,0:13:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}Yugi boy, I know very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.73,0:13:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The two cards you\N have face-down on the field...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...are Ruiz and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...Horn of the Unicorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}I'm positive that in the next turn, you will use this to Combo Attack me with Ruiz...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}If that's a Water-Attribute Monster,\N my set card should be the best choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}Pegasus' set card does worry me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:14:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but I can't let this chance slip by!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}﻿I'll give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.76,0:14:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I switch my set Ruiz to Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I also activate my Set Card,\N Horn of the Unicorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.31,0:14:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His sword becomes an electrical sword and\N ﻿his Attack Points go up by 700 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack the Mermaid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.65,0:14:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You've just made a grave error.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I activate my Trap Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.03,0:14:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}I knew he'd do this...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Mermaid's Tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Mermaid's Tears is a Trap Card that activates\N the ﻿instant the opponent activates a set card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It seals the enemy's attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Ruiz is electrified by his own electricity\N in the bubble of ﻿water,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:15:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and because of it,\N his Attack Points drop back down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I switch the Mermaid to Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Arrow Shot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Ruiz is killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.96,0:15:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It's almost as if he knew what Yugi's ﻿reverse card was going to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.71,0:15:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿So this is Pegasus' Mind Scan...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.55,0:15:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What's Honda doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿He {\i1}still{\i0} isn't back yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Now that you mention it,\N he's taking a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Geez! What the hell's\N he doing at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}As I thought, with Pegasus' Millennium Eye,\N he can see right through me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}That's right, Yugi boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pegasus is not only the creator of the ﻿cards,\N but a king without bounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}How do I fight against\N the power of his Millennium Eye... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:16:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You appear to have\N wasted a turn, Yugi boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.83,0:16:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿There are many variables\N in this game, from ﻿the cards to choose,\N to the right timing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The player's road to defeat\N is lined with a great ﻿number\N of little mistakes, one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Let me tell you one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.76,0:16:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I {\i1}never{\i0} make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.56,0:16:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}Pegasus gives off a sense of absolute ﻿confidence in this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿If I can't break free of that, I can't win!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That Pegasus bastard...!\N {\i1}All{\i0} humans make mistakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he think he's {\i1}God{\i0} or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.74,0:16:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Since Pegasus was the one\N who created ﻿Duel Monsters,\N he's {\i1}almost{\i0} like a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.37,0:16:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The creator knows his world inside out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.25,0:16:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Bakura! Are you trying\N to say Yugi can't win?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I don't think so, but I also don't know\N﻿how anyone can defeat Pegasus...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿No! I believe in Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Croquet-{\i1}sama{\i0} worries far too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿There's no way a motionless brat's just gonna run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.36,0:17:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure it's all right to act like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.82,0:17:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Of course it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.42,0:17:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That was nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.82,0:17:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I set a Monster in Defense Mode\N face-down and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.33,0:18:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}﻿Oi, what's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿This is the head of security.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}﻿Can you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}﻿He's not responding!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The B1 Area has had its lock opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What the hell is he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}﻿You guys, go look for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know what's going on,\N﻿but there may be an intruder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}﻿Hey! Can you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it is an intruder, Pegasus-{\i1}sama{\i0}\N must be told immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.38,0:18:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pegasus-{\i0}sama{\i1} is currently Dueling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I understand. I grant you permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'll let you guys handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.44,0:18:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yugi, concentrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.48,0:18:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Don't back down, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.37,0:18:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Not good! I've been found already...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.43,0:18:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I set a card face-down on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Dragon Egger in Defense Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'll also switch the Mermaid to Defense...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿...and my turn is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.76,0:19:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿This way's no good either...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Wh-what do I do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}Yugi boy is like\N a small animal struggling for breath\N as I crush it with my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.76,0:19:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}For I know every single card\N in your entire hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.03,0:19:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}Mind Scan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}And the card you just drew is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Demon's Summon, isn't that right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:20:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}That gaze that\N pierces through my cards...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.49,0:20:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}This feeling's\N not just my imagination!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿We're counting on you, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.95,0:20:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}He's reading my mind...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.17,0:20:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}But there's nothing\N I can do to stop it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.97,0:20:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Pegasus was really reading through Yugi after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿And Pegasus plays the same ﻿card he used to beat Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.94,0:20:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of Yugi's attacks are working, and even Demon's Summon has become a Soon Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.07,0:20:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yugi's in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.74,0:20:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0} and Honda have gone missing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what's going on in this Duel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.70,0:20:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.58,0:20:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}Attacks Impossible!?\N The Invincible Soon Army"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:21:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The flask shines bright
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}waiting in the Science Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.65,0:21:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By rubbing our cold hands together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.89,0:21:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They will become warm
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.20,0:21:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll shower all over you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.26,0:21:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will support your lonely back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.48,0:21:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.46,0:21:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.12,0:22:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because you're surrounded by a ring of friendship
